org.eclipse.keyple.core.seproxy.plugin

Class AbstractObservablePlugin

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.keyple.core.seproxy.plugin.AbstractPlugin
      • org.eclipse.keyple.core.seproxy.plugin.AbstractObservablePlugin
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ObservablePlugin, ObservablePluginNotifier, ReaderPlugin
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractThreadedObservablePlugin

    public abstract class AbstractObservablePlugin
extends AbstractPlugin
implements ObservablePluginNotifier
    The AbstractObservablePlugin class provides the means to observe a plugin (insertion/removal of readers).
